## 📁 Project Structure

```
financial_audit_env/
├── __init__.py              # Package exports
├── models.py                # Pydantic Action/Observation/State (strict validation)
├── client.py                # EnvClient (OpenEnv + standalone HTTP)
├── baseline.py              # Llama baseline via HF Inference API
├── openenv.yaml             # OpenEnv manifest
├── pyproject.toml           # Package config
├── README.md                ← You are here
├── server/
│   ├── environment.py       # Core reset/step/state logic
│   ├── data_generator.py    # Synthetic financial data with planted errors
│   ├── graders.py           # F1-based deterministic graders
│   ├── tasks.py             # Task definitions (easy/medium/hard)
│   ├── security.py          # Rate limiting, OWASP headers, input validation
│   ├── app.py               # FastAPI server + custom endpoints
│   ├── requirements.txt     # Docker dependencies
│   └── Dockerfile           # Container (non-root, health check)
```

---

## 🔒 Security

- **Rate limiting**: 30 requests/minute per IP on all endpoints
- **Input validation**: Pydantic strict mode, max string lengths, sanitized inputs
- **OWASP headers**: X-Frame-Options, CSP, HSTS, XSS-Protection
- **No stack traces**: Custom error handlers hide internals
- **Non-root Docker**: Container runs as unprivileged user
- **Secure API keys**: Environment variables only, masked in logs

